cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with object recognition and pose estimation using deep learning methods, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN). This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also involves extensive experimentation and analysis of the layers of CNN models, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with multi-view datasets, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
